href=\"#2-background-%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"2 background 이미지 추가하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. background 이미지 추가하기</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>아래 코드 보고 추가 공부 필요</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">image = new image()</code> : 요건 무슨 기능?</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">image.src = &quot;&quot;</code> : 요것도 공부</li>\n<li>\n<p>body에 appendChild로 결국 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;image src&gt;</code> 요걸 넣은건가?</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">function paintImage(imgNumber) {\nconst image = new Image()\nimage.src = `./images/${imgNumber + 1}.jpg`;\nimage.classList.add(&#39;bgImage&#39;)\nbody.appendChild(image)\n}</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-classlistadd\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-classlistadd\" aria-label=\"3 classlistadd permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. classList.add</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>의미 : 특정 element에 class 명을 추가함</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">image.classList.add(&#39;bgImage&#39;)</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"self-study\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#self-study\" aria-label=\"self study permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Self study</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-background-image-넣는법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-background-image-%EB%84%A3%EB%8A%94%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"1 background image 넣는법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. background image 넣는법</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>object.style.backgroundImage = \"url('경로')\"</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">body.style.backgroundImage = &quot;url(&#39;./images/image1.jpg&#39;)&quot;;</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-background-image-꽉차게-하는법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-background-image-%EA%BD%89%EC%B0%A